lly licensed gear from Pro Jersey Sports. Crafted by Mitchell & Ness from 100% polyester mesh, this throwback jersey features premium tackle twill graphics and embroidered details that faithfully recreate the classic design. Side splits at the hem and a woven jock tag add authentic vintage touches, while the breathable mesh construction keeps you comfortable. Brand: Mitchell & Ness Player: Magic Johnson Material: 100% Polyester Machine wash Officially licensed by the NBA',134.99,10,'Basketball','Los Angeles Lakers','Basketball',NULL,'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0378/6653/products/46f18e37d8a1252e5678bea6a959c90b0cff38e2.jpg?v=1759254986','2026-04-25 23:28:06'),(427,'Men\'s Mitchell & Ness Vince Carter Toronto Raptors White 1997-98 Hardwood Classics Swingman Jersey','Vince Carter is one of the greatest dunkers in NBA history, putting the Toronto Raptors on the map with his electrifying 2000 Slam Dunk Contest performance. Half Man, Half Amazing captivated fans worldwide with his jaw-dropping athleticism and became the most beloved player in Raptors franchise history. This Swingman jersey by Mitchell & Ness features tackle twill applique graphics, side splits for comfort and mobility, and a droptail hemline for a classic basketball silhouette. The 100% polyester construction delivers a lightweight, breathable feel, and the jersey is designed to run true to size. Brand: Mitchell & Ness Player: Vince Carter, Guard/Forward Material: 100% Polyester Tackle twill graphics Machine wash Officially licensed by the NBA',134.99,10,'Basketball','Toronto Raptors','Basketball',NULL,'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0378/6653/products/0da4b06bc10a4aa25e60b532def7ab4cf378791a.jpg?v=1762528452','2026-04-25 23:28:06'),(428,'Men\'s Mitchell & Ness Tracy McGrady Toronto Raptors Purple 1998-99 Hardwood Classics Swingman Jersey','Tracy McGrady established himself as one of the most gifted scorers in NBA history during his time with the Toronto Raptors and Orlando Magic. His combinati