ic Finals run. Mitchell & Ness builds this Hardwood Classics Swingman from 100% polyester with tackle twill applique graphics and a mesh body for breathable comfort. The droptail hem with side splits, woven jock tag, and authentic design details replicate the 1996-97 look. Runs true to size with a classic basketball fit. Brand: Mitchell & Ness Hardwood Classics Player: John Stockton (1996-97) Material: 100% polyester mesh Graphics: Tackle twill applique Care: Machine wash, line dry Officially licensed NBA product',134.99,10,'Basketball','Utah Jazz','Basketball',NULL,'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0378/6653/products/b8c12d989425a9b27c761d8f9fcc4bae8f0fb111.jpg?v=1762528438','2026-04-25 23:28:06'),(436,'Men\'s Karl Malone Utah Jazz Mitchell & Ness 1996-97 Hardwood Classics Swingman Jersey','Karl Malone earned his second NBA MVP award during the 1996-97 season, averaging 27.4 points and 9.9 rebounds while leading the Utah Jazz to the NBA Finals. \"The Mailman\" retired as the league\'s second all-time leading scorer with 36,928 points, and his pick-and-roll partnership with John Stockton remains the most lethal two-man game in basketball history. This Mitchell & Ness Hardwood Classics Swingman jersey is constructed from 100% polyester with tackle twill applique graphics for premium, raised name and number detailing. The droptail hem and side splits provide comfortable range of motion, while the woven jock tag and classic Jazz purple mountain design deliver era-authentic styling. Brand: Mitchell & Ness Player: Karl Malone #32 Material: 100% polyester Tackle twill applique graphics Droptail hem with side splits Machine wash, line dry Officially licensed NBA product',99.99,10,'Basketball','Utah Jazz','Basketball',NULL,'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0378/6653/products/fff5086e2d97dbcbdef0a882d1c1436aa7c0f1af.jpg?v=1762528438','2026-04-25 23:28:06'),(437,'Men\'s Miami Heat Alonzo Mourning Mitchell & Ness Black 1996-97 Hardwood Classics Swingman Jersey','Alonzo Mourning anchored the Miami Heat during their rise to Eastern Conference contention in the late 1990s, averaging 21.3 points, 9.9 rebounds, and an NBA-leading 3.9 blocks per game during the 1996-97 season. \"Zo\" won two Defensive Player of the Year awards and eventually captured a championship ring with Miami in 2006, becoming one of the most beloved players in Heat history. This Mitchell & Ness Hardwood Classics Swingman jersey is crafted from 100% polyester with tackle twill applique graphics that replicate the 1996-97 black alternate design. The droptail hem and side splits at the hem provide authentic basketball jersey styling. A woven jock tag adds an official finishing detail. Machine wash, line dry. Brand: Mitchell & Ness, Hardwood Classics Player: Alonzo Mourning #33, Miami Heat (1996-97) Material: 100% polyester Tackle twill applique graphics Droptail hem with side splits Machine wash, line dry Officially licensed NBA product',99.99,10,'Basketball','Miami Heat','Basketball',NULL,'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0378/6653/products/095aa74baa0b974363295b61d69179d3384a49fd.jpg?v=1762528428','2026-04-25 23:28:06'),(438,'Men\'s Shawn Kemp Seattle Supersonics Mitchell & Ness 1996-96 Green NBA Swingman Hardwood Classics Jersey','Shawn Kemp is the Reign Man, whose ferocious dunking and athleticism alongside Gary Payton made the \'90s Sonics appointment television. This jersey captures the impact of a player who has become a defining figure for the franchise. This Mitchell & Ness Hardwood Classics swingman jersey is made from 100% polyester with tackle twill applique graphics for a premium layered look. The droptail design, side splits at the hem, and jock tag deliver authentic court-ready detail. Runs true to size; order one size up for a looser fit. Brand: Mitchell & Ness Player: Shawn Kemp, Power Forward Material: 100% Polyester Tackle twill applique graphics Machine wash Officially licensed by the NBA',134.99,10,'Basketball','Seattle Supersonics','Basketball',NULL